  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add onions and garlic, cooking until softened and fragrant, about 5 minutes.",
    "Drain soaked butter beans and add them to the skillet. Stir well to coat with the onion mixture.",
    "Stir in tomatoes, paprika, cumin, salt, and pepper. Reduce heat to low and simmer for about 30 minutes or until flavors have melded and beans are tender.",
    "Serve hot as a side dish or main course."
